query:
SELECT ps.projectId, ps.criteriaId, ps.score, pc.name, pc.weight 
FROM project_scores ps 
JOIN prioritization_criteria pc ON ps.criteriaId = pc.id 
WHERE pc.isActive = 1 
LIMIT 10;
